{"tid":277708,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【Uber筆戰】創科局又被KO 李兆富：「咁大陸又真係快過香港喎」","createTime":"2017-06-09T23:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T02:22:39.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0fb7887b1b3239d24c69fbe113660fd2d789b7","tid":277708,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1497020226_d560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1497020226_d560.jpg&h=9df96f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長楊偉雄，近日就Uber合法性問題，向公共政策顧問李兆富下筆戰戰書。正當李兆富已再發文反擊楊偉雄討論失焦時，創新及科技局局於Facebook發帖，狠批Uber知法犯法！<br />\n<br />\n然而，李兆富重申的兩條問題，即政府究竟有何具體指標，去判斷何謂「大多數人意見」；以及政府可有計劃在可見將來就「不合時宜的法例」進行公眾諮詢及公開討論，當局均未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n其後Uber一句回應「KO」創科局，指「全球包括中國、新加坡、澳洲等超過100個政府，已就汽車共乘立法，我們相信有可行的法律框架將此嶄新服務在香港納入規管。」而創科局的Facebook可見，網民的反應一面倒批評局方的說法，出post後8小時，「嬲嬲」數目超過2000個，直逼本身專頁的2600個like。<br />\n<br />\n李兆富認為，楊偉雄避開筆戰，到facebook出post是因為「回歸廿周年之前，各政府部門都唔想生事端嘅本來，但係呢，ITB 又要證明自己嘅立場都有民意，整個 post 啦，點知會畀人洗版。」<br />\n<br />\n對於Uber 的回應，他指「咁大陸又真係快過香港喎，香港警察拉人個日，深圳剛剛發牌畀網約車」。他指，Uber的問題在於「香港好多法例都形成一群既得利益者，但係香港又真係有選委同功能組別嘅設計，政府都唔敢去改；我相信政府心知肚明，但冇辦法，因為行政主導。」<br />\n<br />\n李兆富指，「其實政府只要好似標時又或者當年工資立法咁，畀唔同持份者民間拆解，最後政府都係做超然嘅裁判角色，咁樣香港係可以 move forward。」但今次「創科局最錯就係企去是但一邊，如果唔係都唔會咁大反彈。」<br />\n<br />\n給楊偉雄的公開信（公共政策顧問　李兆富）<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sgT33V \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sgT33V%20&d=miRruejfEI4R7cScey8rnPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=b5c7afe3\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sgT33V </a><br />\n回應李兆富的公開信 （創新及科技局局長 楊偉雄）<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2siVwLa \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2siVwLa%20&d=miRruejfEI4R7cScey8rnPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=588a3ef0\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2siVwLa </a><br />\n創新及科技局最大責任是制定法規 －－回覆楊偉雄公開信 （公共政策顧問 李兆富）<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2r2l9fq \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2r2l9fq%20&d=miRruejfEI4R7cScey8rnPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=b3734cdf\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2r2l9fq </a>・<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56808046&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56808046%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170609&d=miRruejfEI4R7cScey8rnPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=03f01050\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56808046%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170609&h=42485b73\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56808046&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170609</a>"},{"pid":"0b773cac359f3b6cce8684b548809233ba5f3975","tid":277708,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:38:23.000Z","msg":"政府反對我贊成，支持uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13827c43ce2cb24ca55b8d2dd2f8b9666852d922","tid":277708,"uid":61752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}